data.description: CHARMING CITY HOME!! 1296 sqft 3 bed 1 bath home on an oversized city lot (.25 acres). Larger living room, spacious kitchen with lots of counter and storage space. Good sized bedrooms, laundry/utility room. Patio space out back, alley access, large fully landscaped yard and so much more!! Tenant occupied, needs 24 hour notice to show.  Subject to court approval.
